data.description: Price Improvement!  Don't miss this all-brick ranch home on a corner nestled in west Loveland. This all-brick ranch style home is ready for its new owners. Sitting just west of Lake Loveland and a short distance to Mehaffey Park there are plenty of outside activities to enjoy! This home has been well maintained over time. Examples include a new roof, updated windows and newer boiler. Other features of this 3 bedroom, 1  3/4 bath home include a cozy gas fireplace in the living room, great kitchen counter space, a partially finished basement, and a 431 sq. ft. garage. Don't miss this opportunity and schedule your private showing today! Home is being sold "As Is".
